headline: 5 Multiline Insurers Stocks to Watch Amid Increased Digitalization
summary: Better pricing, product redesigns and technological advancements are expected to aid Zacks Multiline Insurance industry players like AIG, PRU, PFG, EG and AIZ.

headline: Trinity Life Sciences Secures Prestigious Leader Position in Everest Group’s 2025 PEAK Matrix® for Life Sciences AI & Analytics Excellence
summary: WALTHAM, Mass., August 07, 2025--Trinity Life Sciences, a leader in advisory, insights and analytics for the life sciences industry, today announced its recognition as a Leader in Everest Group’s 2025 PEAK Matrix® for Life Sciences AI and Analytics. Trinity Life Sciences was one of only ten companies to achieve Leader status.
